{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Olive Tapenade","content":["Place all tapenade ingredients in mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula, then chop again <b>3 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl."]},{"title":"Tortilla","content":["Place Parmesan in mixing bowl and grate <b>5 sec\/speed 9<b>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside. Rinse and dry mixing bowl.","Place onion, oil, garlic and parsley in mixing bowl then chop <b>3 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula, then sauté <b>2 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Transfer into a large ceramic or glass bowl and set aside.","Place water in mixing bowl. Place Varoma dish into position then weigh potato, mushrooms (optional) and red pepper into it. Secure Varoma lid and steam <b>15 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Remove Varoma and transfer steamed vegetables into the large ceramic or glass  bowl with onion mixture. Empty mixing bowl.","Preheat grill to 200°C.","Place all remaining ingredients in mixing bowl and mix <b>10 sec\/speed 4<b>, then transfer into large ceramic or glass bowl with other ingredients and stir to combine using spatula.","Grease an ovenproof frying pan (Ø 26 cm) with oil and place over medium heat. Transfer mixture from ceramic or glass bowl into the frying pan and ensure vegetables are evenly spread out.","Sprinkle over reserved Parmesan cheese, then reduce heat to low and cook for 6-8 minutes or until the eggs are set on the bottom of the tortilla yet still slightly runny on top.","Remove frying pan from hob and place under the grill for 2-3 minutes or until eggs on top of tortilla are just set and starting to turn golden.","Remove from under the grill and allow tortilla to rest in frying pan for 2-3 minutes. Carefully remove tortilla from frying pan onto a chopping board with aid of spatula.","Cut tortilla into 8 wedges, then serve immediately with reserved olive tapenade on the side."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Olive Tapenade","content":["50 g pitted black olives","50 g pitted green olives","2 sun-dried tomatoes, drained","1 Tbsp pickled capers, drained","5 fresh basil leaves","2 pinches ground smoked paprika","1 tsp balsamic vinegar"]},{"title":"Tortilla","content":["50 g Parmesan cheese, cut in pieces (3 cm)","80 g red onion, quartered","1 tbsp olive oil, plus extra for greasing","2 garlic cloves","4 sprigs fresh flat-leaf parsley, leaves only","500 g water","200 g new potatoes, peeled, cut into halves lengthways and cut into slices (0.5 cm)","40 - 60 g fresh mushrooms, cleaned and sliced (optional)","80 g red pepper, deseeded and cut into strips (0.5 cm)","½ tsp ground paprika","¼ - ½ tsp fine sea salt, to taste","¼ - ½ tsp ground black pepper, to taste","6 large eggs","50 g whole milk"]}],"id":"r123525","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-m-TwdrLHKYY\/XZMvs9GyO8I\/AAAAAAAAaVM\/YIg8rUqsHLkKyu6oA6SVLxm7op_6mMfDQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_ngZ4WWmtEFM9g_Y-.png","title":"Red Pepper and Potato Tortillas with Olive Tapenade","publishedAt":"2017-04-24T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"9.7 g","fat":"11 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"5.6 g","calories":"687 kJ \/ 164 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large glass bowl, tongs or slotted spoon, oven-proof frying pan (approx. Ø 26 cm), ovenproof frying pan (26 cm), chopping block , grill, hob","basicInfo":["easy","20m","35m","8 portions"]}